{"tid":307172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習總以為係演員？獲習握手90後新移民警起底","createTime":"2017-07-03T06:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:30:04.000Z","uid":35790,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eff185cdecb5a0a382d6a2b1ec9c76bef707c111","tid":307172,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"習總以為係演員？獲習握手90後新移民警起底<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平訪港3日期間，到八鄉參觀少年警訊永久活動中心暨青少年綜合訓練營，其間警方安排習總，接見一名在內地出生的男警員。該名男警向習近平說：「主席，請你放心，我一定會努力工作。做一個愛國家、愛香港的好警察。」習近平隨即問道：「這是正式錄用的警察嗎？之前要上警校嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民近日回顧此新聞片段，有人認為習主席此話的潛台詞是「呢個老臨做到真嘅一樣樣！堅喎」，亦有人笑言該警員「假到一個點呢，連主子都唔信」，還是習總「心水清」，「一眼看穿是戲子」。<br />\n<br />\n《CUP媒體》昨午上載該男警的單頭照至facebook，透露其背景資料。原來獲習接見和握手的那位新移民警員，叫「叶健文」，現年22歲，於廣東茂名出生。名字沿用簡體字「叶」，而非正體字「葉」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170703/56906411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170703%2F56906411&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4274cc2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170703%2F56906411&h=7dfc87de\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170703/56906411</a>"},{"pid":"5b41decea6ce00526c1c8cf7bfeae55044663bca","tid":307172,"uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"臨時演員都係演員"},{"pid":"c48c7b26852ac6c3b435630d5f5fb4b6a7cad567","tid":307172,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"冒警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1fc46841f57252d91fdccb8201577daece409c","tid":307172,"uid":427,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffdf2c0a685faaaa5507012c3170d09c909df40","tid":307172,"uid":81569,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"屌你班撚樣咪當習主席係傻啦<br />\n習主席自己都打仔出身有咩未見過<br />\n一眼睇撚穿啦"},{"pid":"d7cc433e514e742e5a6ffba2fde54ef99344e4b7","tid":307172,"uid":37661,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"完全一啲廣東樣都冇。<br />\n<br />\n九成九死北佬南下打嘅賤種。"},{"pid":"e53d18b606f298b5ba56bde6247b57cb784c1d38","tid":307172,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"成個支那人樣"},{"pid":"e0b88effb1fe74126876c110021642718252f236","tid":307172,"uid":46454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"真正連狗奴才都未識做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22406a0576b8c7cdf8a61df2b7b48f3e1621c020","tid":307172,"uid":2638,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>完全一啲廣東樣都冇。<br />\n<br />\n九成九死北佬南下打嘅賤種。</blockquote><br />\nAGGER<br />\n湖南樣"},{"pid":"bb8b88a248867143c2126d92a1fefad2d1c96e40","tid":307172,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"撈樣"},{"pid":"5ec6ca66383dafd2393ce3de5f06960d50ea6fb0","tid":307172,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>完全一啲廣東樣都冇。<br />\n<br />\n九成九死北佬南下打嘅賤種。</blockquote><br />\nAGGER<br />\n湖南樣</blockquote><br />\n老早應該長江為界，支那38線，<br />\n<br />\n北共產 南國民(資本)，之後個情況就同南北韓一撚樣，咁就啱"},{"pid":"8d86ca366d26f80a0e006c9b5743a470fd8e2fdf","tid":307172,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"點解大陸仔塊面咁多墨屎"},{"pid":"34dd2f11df0e05d1669b343e9a14a01a92206bfe","tid":307172,"uid":8681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>完全一啲廣東樣都冇。<br />\n<br />\n九成九死北佬南下打嘅賤種。</blockquote><br />\nAGGER<br />\n湖南